summary: This is a brief email exchange from June 30, 2020, where someone requests a copy of the indictment against Ghislaine Maxwell. The email includes an attachment of the signed and stamped indictment document.

events.title: Email Request for Maxwell Indictment
events.description: An email is sent requesting a copy of the indictment against Ghislaine Maxwell, with the signed and stamped indictment attached.

keyFacts: An email dated June 30, 2020, references the indictment against Ghislaine Maxwell (Case 20-Cr.-33).
The attached file is the signed and stamped version of the indictment.
The correspondence is a simple request for a copy of the legal document.
